OL,3,CConsumer confidence up in June amid
OL,4,C'dark shadow' of inflation and war
OL,6,FConsumer confidence improved
OL,7,Fmarginally in June despite the "dark
OL,8,Fshadow" of inflation and turmoil in
OL,9,Fthe Middle East, figures show.
OL,11,FGfK's long-running Consumer Confidence
OL,12,FIndex rose two points but remains
OL,13,Ffirmly in negative territory at minus
OL,14,F18.
OL,16,FConfidence in the general economy over
OL,17,Fthe coming year rose five points,
OL,18,Fdriving the improvement, but still
OL,19,Fremains at minus 28 ` 17 points worse
OL,20,Fthan last June.
