OL,6,FThe forecast for personal finances
OL,7,Fover the next 12 months remained
OL,8,Funchanged at positive two ` two points
OL,9,Fdown on this time last year.
OL,11,FThe major purchase index, an indicator
OL,12,Fof confidence in buying big ticket
OL,13,Fitems, also remained unchanged at
OL,14,Fminus 16, seven points better than
OL,15,Flast June.
