OL,3,CConsumer confidence up in June amid
OL,4,C'dark shadow' of inflation and war
OL,6,FNeil Bellamy, consumer insights
OL,7,Fdirector at GfK, said: "Consumers have
OL,8,Fbeen resolute in their views on their
OL,9,Fwallets, with June's personal
OL,10,Ffinancial situation scores ` past and
OL,11,Ffuture ` unchanged from May.
OL,13,F"Yet confidence is still fragile
OL,14,Fbecause the dark shadow of inflation
OL,15,Fis a day-to-day challenge for so many
OL,16,Fof us.
