OL,3,CConsumer confidence up in June amid
OL,4,C'dark shadow' of inflation and war
OL,6,F"With petrol prices set to rise in the
OL,7,Fcoming weeks following the escalation
OL,8,Fof the conflict in the Middle East,
OL,9,Fand with ongoing uncertainty as to the
OL,10,Ffull impact of tariffs, there is still
OL,11,Fmuch that could negatively impact
OL,12,Fconsumers.
OL,14,F"With so much volatility, now is
OL,15,Fcertainly not the time to hope for the
OL,16,Fproverbial 'light at the end of the
OL,17,Ftunnel'."
